Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.51,0:02:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是亲眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座小镇里  有着充满了谜团的杀人集团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在此居住有什么问题的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.61,0:02:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆就回旧市好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚他绝不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且是先给您一个忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.27,0:02:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请再给我们一些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今我们都没有过…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你们应该已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年比较特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们想一家人一起克服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然您这么说  那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄同学  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无变化的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平凡的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总觉得发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你惊吓过度了  博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我提前来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  居然丢下她了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃一定生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  难道说和小铃吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  博士君有些地方还是很迟钝的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定已经惹小铃生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  博士君？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎你觉得我是个麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你的叔父
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个中心的栉名田院长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说我是个奇怪的人什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  如果有什么话要和我说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃请假了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天也精神地开始上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时把一诚关在家里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说  我们家人必须做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十铃也同意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子说不定要不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还有胶囊什么的  一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的没错  家人一起克服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十铃  你也要当心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  五十铃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果连你也有什么事的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看老哥的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥  不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿胶囊来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  你也需要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联防队那些家伙来过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.53,0:06:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  之前有说过嫦娥镇流传的都市传说的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个还有些怎么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在镇上的食人鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病院的幽灵病房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排成队伍的红色萤火虫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响彻半夜的野兽叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些类似的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在镇上的食人鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是这个城镇里住着怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们会袭击人这样的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据传闻怪物半夜在镇上徘徊寻找食物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没有人烟的地方袭击人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样袭击的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是从人的口中直接吸取生气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得像是猎奇电影一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我有些事想和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是一个传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都市传说的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着大镰刀的少女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  昨晚真的看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:07:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个少女袭击人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是想去报警的  但却没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上又去了现场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事件的痕迹却完全不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  拿着大镰刀的少女的传闻什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的都市传说听过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个没有听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是这事听起来挺有趣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为博士君来说  算是不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不错什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有这样的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是「有其父必有其子」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…这可不是我瞎编的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不过还是继续说给我听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好再说说那个拿着大镰刀的少女的角色特点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能让故事更有趣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:09:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  小铃怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以前都不怎么请假的  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去时我去看望一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥  吃晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  工作有进展吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  走三步退二步的感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒退怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  最近遇到难关了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了  这里的传说中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关于拿着大镰刀的少女的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话去问同班同学那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要同学是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  小要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她擅长的领域吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要同学也说不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我更不可能知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但姑且会调查一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮到哥哥收拾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  今天不是麻奈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是替过你一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘记了  是是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了寻找1年前遗弃在南极的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还…还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太郎  小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是食物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对饥饿的两条猛犬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能活下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影  结局——南极物语
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近日即将公开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看完电影后的用餐可选择离本院徒步1分钟的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡店  艾特兰泽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡店  艾  特  兰  泽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八朔~ 八朔~ 嫦娥的八朔~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸呀~ 酸呀~ 呀呀呀呀呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去丢下垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一诚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是一诚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说会从人的口中吸取生气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被杀的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为会这样  我们才忠告你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:14:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我  前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是谁？  放手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.66,0:15:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你安分点  我们便不会动粗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟我们走一趟么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈他呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.77,0:15:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和…  摘花前辈他一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据戒律  摘花一诚先生他应当很快就会受到制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且  你也已经不再是迄今为止的那个你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:15:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是爽毙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么爽的事  为什么我一直以来都得忍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝过了这味道  就再也回不去原先的世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回你个头！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠天之神  除之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(326,434)\fs24}狼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥…！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚前辈他…  怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有些疯狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样根本就无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是眠吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联防队町田先生叫我传个话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被摘花一诚变成「神人」的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石我木雅美  请叔父大人处置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那边  明天就由我亲自来说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小眠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也挺不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃她  今天也休息么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说  哥你被她甩了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑  玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不走的话  可要迟到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去叫下她？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她真不太舒服  还在睡的话  可就打扰她了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.19,0:18:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…  太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十铃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此  你也别再护着一诚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会说出那么冷淡的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是一家人么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  五十铃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不想连你也一并失去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:18:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是戒律
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胶囊的事应该是机密事项
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又是怎么查出来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这世上  知晓消息的人只要超过了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便不可能保密
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打的是什么算盘？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的又是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是一早就说了的么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想助院长您一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  就像你们医生为了解患者的病情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要借助病历卡一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的新药  也得靠着数据来开发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄君  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:19:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:19:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃她呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天就没有联系过你么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她家  你也没去？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  没去成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是发生了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也精神地开始上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.01,0:20:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  安静
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐回座位上去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我迟到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  摘花  正好迟到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可让我担心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  就先点名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  感冒好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…  昨天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.90,0:21:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.87,0:21:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.02,0:21:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.59,0:21:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚前辈他搬家了…  这…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.14,0:22:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  小铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥他被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.24,0:22:17.81,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}忘れないで　この思いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.24,0:22:17.81,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}勿忘怀  此相思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.85,0:22:28.51,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕らが信じた愛の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.85,0:22:28.51,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}吾等深信之情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.65,0:22:34.76,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}抱きしめた夜には
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.65,0:22:34.76,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}拥夜入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.81,0:22:37.62,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}影が月でなく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.81,0:22:37.62,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}影非月  月非影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:41.00,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}繰り返す罪には
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:41.00,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}罪劫轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.04,0:22:49.55,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}戸惑いの月が満ちる　融ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.04,0:22:49.55,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}盈惑月  消无痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:56.39,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いくつものこころが　君を縛るなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:56.39,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}千千心结若缚君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.75,0:23:07.00,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}堕ちて行く決意が許されるまで　愛なのと信じたり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.75,0:23:07.00,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}则深信此爱  直至神允  坠天之志
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.73,0:23:14.33,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}かすかな声手繰り寄せて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.73,0:23:14.33,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}细语声中忆往昔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:20.12,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}交わる闇の調べ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:20.12,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爱恨交织暗之乐
